1) Yale Database: .gif format 
   image dimension : 320*243 pixels
   file size : ranges between 26 to 69 kb	 	
   download url : http://www.cs.princeton.edu/courses/archive/spr03/cs496/images/
   No of Images = 165
   No of classes = 15
   Images per class = 11	

2) Yale Database: .pgm format 
   image dimension : 320*243 pixels
   file size : 76 kb
   download url : http://www.cs.uml.edu/~giam/91.580.203/Projects/DGabriel/dat/yalefaces/yalefaces%20%28copy%29/
   No of Images = 165
   No of classes = 15
   Images per class = 11

3) Resized yale Database or cropped yale : .gif format  ( This is given by Prof.GTS )
   image dimension : 92*112 pixels
   file size : around 10.2-11 kb
   download url : http://www.mediafire.com/?uy8435aji57pd26
   No of Images = 165
   No of classes = 15
   Images per class = 11
 	

4) ORL Database : .pgm format
   image dimension : 92*112 pixels
   file size : around 10.2-11 kb
   download url : http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/Research/DTG/attarchive/pub/data/att_faces.zip	
   No of Images = 400
   No of classes = 40
   Images per class = 10
